data.description: Discover this delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with oversized one-car attached garage near the heart of Westminster, Colorado! Located in a well-maintained HOA community where pride of ownership shows, you’ll appreciate the well-manicured curb appeal and a serene neighborhood ambiance. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a cozy living space that flows into the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and the adjacent dining area opens to the backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Two cozy bedrooms offer ample closet space (one is a walk-in closet) and the full bathroom is tastefully designed. Notable features include a brand NEW ROOF, central cooling and heating, and a recently-serviced furnace for peace of mind. This neighborhood is ideal for dog lovers, with great walking opportunities, and your furry friends will appreciate the fenced-in backyard. Convenience is at your doorstep, with schools, parks, grocery stores, shopping, and dining options nearby. Golf enthusiasts will relish the proximity to golf courses, and fitness centers are readily accessible. The city center, just 1.3 miles or 5 minutes away, provides access to entertainment and cultural attractions. Plus, commuting is a breeze with major highways and public transportation options nearby. Whether you're a first-time buyer, downsizing, or seeking an investment property, this turn-key residence offers a welcoming and convenient lifestyle in a community where pride of ownership is evident at every turn. Schedule a showing today and make this delightful Westminster gem your new home!
